From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: PlazaMC <dev@plazamc.org>
Date: Tue, 7 Jul 2026 18:05:00 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] Slime World ServerLevel hooks

Adds the minimal hooks required for PlazaSlimeLevelInstance to extend
ServerLevel: a bootstrap-aware constructor, a field to hold the in-memory
Slime world, and a generator hook used by SlimeLevelGenerator.

diff --git a/net/minecraft/server/level/ServerLevel.java b/net/minecraft/server/level/ServerLevel.java
index a795ceebd304d7c4bba2a48b7722e1cc464366f2..8c9e3a61ae8ac1b683b8d19ea487b3713d1e17db 100644
--- a/net/minecraft/server/level/ServerLevel.java
+++ b/net/minecraft/server/level/ServerLevel.java
@@ -305,8 +305,8 @@ public class ServerLevel extends Level implements ServerEntityGetter, WorldGenLe
